Title: Epigenomic tools
Author: Mark Robinson <mark.robinson@imls.uzh.ch>, Dario Strbenac <d.strbenac@garvan.org.au>, Aaron Statham <a.statham@garvan.org.au>, Andrea Riebler <andrea.riebler@math.ntnu.no>
